"{\"uid\": \"rappler.com-sports-katie-ledecky-says-faith-anti-doping-all-time-low-ahead-paris-olympics-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  SUMMARY  This is AI generated summarization, which may have errors.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 69, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 21, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999946859561757, \"rank\": 4.0701151956854804e-06, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For context, always refer to the full article.\", \"from\": 70, \"to\": 116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"THUMBS UP.\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 128, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Katie Ledecky of the U.S. celebrates after winning the women's 800m freestyle final in the 2023 World Aquatics Championships.\", \"from\": 129, \"to\": 254, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 129, \"end\": 142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marko Djurica/REUTERS  Seven-time Olympic gold medallist Katie Ledecky has said her faith in the anti-doping system ahead of the Paris Games is at an all-time low amid the widely-criticized handling of failed drug tests in Chinese swimming.\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 496, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 313, \"end\": 326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}, {\"begin\": 479, \"end\": 486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9945902284109462, \"rank\": 0.004656919283415977, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In excerpts from an interview with \\\"CBS News Sunday Morning\\\" that will air this weekend, Ledecky spoke about the 23 Chinese swimmers who avoided sanctions after testing positive for a banned substance months before the Tokyo Olympics held in 2021.\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 534, \"end\": 557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News_Sunday_Morning\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CBS News Sunday Morning\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News_Sunday_Morning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News_Sunday_Morning\"}, {\"begin\": 614, \"end\": 621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9945902284109462, \"rank\": 0.004656919283415977, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's hard going into Paris knowing that we are going to be racing some of these athletes,\\\" said Ledecky.\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 769, \"end\": 774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998008561505, \"rank\": 1.9914386070448484e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I think our faith in some of the systems is at an all-time low.\\\"\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 922, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You try not to think too much about (it) when you are actually racing.\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And the best thing to do is to just go out there and try to win.\\\"\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1061, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's tough when you have in the back of your head that it's not necessarily an even playing field.\\\"\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"China's anti-doping agency cleared the swimmers of wrongdoing before the Tokyo Olympics, deciding the positive tests were the result of being inadvertently exposed to the banned substance through contamination.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1165, \"end\": 1170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.6074167050005308, \"rank\": 0.6398742492097598, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A report determined all the swimmers who tested positive were staying at the same hotel where traces of a banned heart medication called trimetazidine (TMZ) were discovered in the kitchen.\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1565, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The World Anti-Doping Agency (WADA), which accepted China's finding in 2021, said in April\\u00a0it wouldlaunch an independent reviewof the case amid pressure from athletes and national anti-doping authorities.\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1571, \"end\": 1602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Anti-Doping Agency (WADA)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\"}, {\"begin\": 1571, \"end\": 1602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Anti-Doping Agency (WADA)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\"}, {\"begin\": 1619, \"end\": 1624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.6074167050005308, \"rank\": 0.6398742492097598, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WADA vigorously defended\\u00a0its initial handling of the case and said it had no evidence to question China's finding that the swimmers were inadvertently contaminated by TMZ.\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1944, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1871, \"end\": 1876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.6074167050005308, \"rank\": 0.6398742492097598, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In this instance, it does not seem like everything was followed to a tee.\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 2020, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, I'd like to see some accountability here,\\\" Ledecky said in the interview.\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2098, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I'd like to see some answers as to why this happened the way it did.\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2169, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I'd really like to see that steps are taken for the future so that we can regain some confidence in the global system.\\\"\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2293, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics, which would be Ledecky's fourth, begins on July 26.- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2299, \"end\": 2313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\